<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢你昨天帮忙<delay8 />
送来圣诞老人的礼物。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />礼物是有趣的玩具家具哦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让我回想起许多小时候发生的事情，<delay8 />
一时间沉浸在乡愁之中呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">昨天圣诞老人给我的礼物<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如我期待的一样，<delay8 />是很棒的玩具家具。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
谢谢你为我<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />将礼物送来。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
谢谢你昨天<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和我交换了礼物！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我准备的礼物<delay8 />还合你的心意吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我担心你会不会觉得
有点太孩子气了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢你昨天送我礼物。<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能够在平安夜交换礼物，<delay8 />
感觉我们的关系已经非常亲密<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很开心！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
昨天辛苦你了！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既要帮忙分发圣诞老人的礼物，<delay8 />
又要和大家交换礼物<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的表现真棒！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天，我得到了圣诞老人的礼物，<delay8 />
还有<tag a="110" b="4" />的礼物，
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就好像做梦一样～<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天发生的事不是梦，<delay20 />
而是现实，没错吧？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />平安夜过得开心吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />美味佳肴
吃得太多了，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现在正在反省。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">昨天是平安夜，<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />，
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你吃蛋糕了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />圣诞蛋糕<delay20 />无论在平安夜吃，
还是在圣诞节当天吃，<delay8 />再不然两天都吃，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都很美味哦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
